                           Pandd Core Change Log
                           =====================

Version 1.3.0 (2013-12-16)
--------------------------

- Chg: ApiGen replaces Doxygen as API documentation generator

Version 1.2.0 (2013-08-20)
--------------------------

- New: Added code quality ant task to run all check except syntaxcheck and phpunit 

Version 1.1.0 (2013-01-24)
--------------------------

- New: Ant tasks for use of code quality testing tools (PHPUnit, PHPMD, PHPCPD etc.)
- New: Support for non-JAR artifacts

Version 1.0.0 (2012-07-11)
--------------------------

- first production release